[t2].[CreationTime], [t2].[CreatorUserId], [t2].[DeleterUserId], [t2].[DeletionTime], [t2].[Description], [t2].[EducationLevel], [t2].[ExperienceYearsCount], [t2].[IsClosed], [t2].[IsDeleted], [t2].[LastModificationTime], [t2].[LastModifierUserId], [t2].[MaxSalary], [t2].[MinSalary], [t2].[RequiredEmployeesCount], [t2].[Slug], [t2].[Status], [t2].[Title], [t2].[WorkAvailbility], [t2].[WorkEngagement], [t2].[WorkLevel], [t3].[Id], [t3].[CityId], [t3].[CreationTime], [t3].[CreatorUserId], [t3].[DateOfEstablishment], [t3].[DeleterUserId], [t3].[DeletionTime], [t3].[IsActive], [t3].[IsDeleted], [t3].[JobType], [t3].[LastModificationTime], [t3].[LastModifierUserId], [t3].[NumberOfEmployees], [t3].[ReasonRefuse], [t3].[Status], [t3].[UserId], [t3].[WebSite], [t4].[Id], [t4].[About], [t4].[Address], [t4].[CoreId], [t4].[CreationTime], [t4].[CreatorUserId], [t4].[DeleterUserId], [t4].[DeletionTime], [t4].[IsDeleted], [t4].[Language], [t4].[LastModificationTime], [t4].[LastModifierUserId], [t4].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT [w].[Id], [w].[CreationTime], [w].[CreatorUserId], [w].[DeletedByCompany], [w].[DeleterUserId], [w].[DeletionTime], [w].[Description], [w].[IsDeleted], [w].[LastModificationTime], [w].[LastModifierUserId], [w].[ProfileId], [w].[RejectReason], [w].[Status], [w].[WorkPostId]
    FROM [WorkApplications] AS [w]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [w].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ORDER BY [w].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[About], [p].[CityId], [p].[CreationTime], [p].[CreatorUserId], [p].[DeleterUserId], [p].[DeletionTime], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[LastModificationTime], [p].[LastModifierUserId], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [Profiles] AS [p]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProfileId] = [t0].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[AuthenticationSource], [a].[CompanyId], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[DialCode], [a].[EmailAddress], [a].[EmailConfirmationCode], [a].[FcmToken], [a].[InvitationCode], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsEmailConfirmed], [a].[IsLockoutEnabled], [a].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[Password], [a].[PasswordResetCode], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[ProfileId], [a].[RegistrationFullName], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[Surname], [a].[TenantId], [a].[Type], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AbpUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_4)
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[UserId] = [t1].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [w0].[Id], [w0].[ApplicantsCount], [w0].[CompanyId], [w0].[CreationTime], [w0].[CreatorUserId], [w0].[DeleterUserId], [w0].[DeletionTime], [w0].[Description], [w0].[EducationLevel], [w0].[ExperienceYearsCount], [w0].[IsClosed], [w0].[IsDeleted], [w0].[LastModificationTime], [w0].[LastModifierUserId], [w0].[MaxSalary], [w0].[MinSalary], [w0].[RequiredEmployeesCount], [w0].[Slug], [w0].[Status], [w0].[Title], [w0].[WorkAvailbility], [w0].[WorkEngagement], [w0].[WorkLevel]
    FROM [WorkPosts] AS [w0]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_5 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [w0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t2] ON [t].[WorkPostId] = [t2].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CityId], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DateOfEstablishment], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[JobType], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[NumberOfEmployees], [c].[ReasonRefuse], [c].[Status], [c].[UserId], [c].[WebSite]
    FROM [Companies] AS [c]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_6 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[CompanyId] = [t3].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[About], [c0].[Address], [c0].[CoreId], [c0].[CreationTime], [c0].[CreatorUserId], [c0].[DeleterUserId], [c0].[DeletionTime], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[Language], [c0].[LastModificationTime], [c0].[LastModifierUserId], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [CompanyTranslations] AS [c0]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_7 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [c0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[CoreId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreationTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t3].[Id]
